Author: heavensdoor90
Text: This is me. I’ll go for months eating 600 calories or less and then get stuck in a solid month or two eating till I literally hurt and am hiding how much food I’m eating. Ah - then laxatives and cleanse teas. :(

Author: troll_beast
Text: I’m stuck in the same cycle.  Binge.  Starve.  Binge.  Starve.  Repeat.
